wastes compute

Bad compression

scrollbar inefficient

Meaning lost.

⸻

The real distinction

You’re describing two different editing goals.

Efficient phrasing
	•	remove filler
	•	preserve meaning

Forced compression
	•	reduce length
	•	meaning may degrade

So your instinct is correct.

